reviewText: If possible I would have rated this with negative stars. The video quality is mediocre as is  the audio. Also, it is by no means "complete" as it does not address disassembly of the slide only routine maintenance and disassembly of only the frame

I had viewed a number of pieces of this DVD on youtube, but it's great to have them all assembled on a DVD.  EXTREMELY clear and informative steps to help with many armorer and upgrade tasks.  With this information I have become comfortable with COMPLETE dis-assembly, parts replacement, and re assembly of my 92 series pistols.
This is an excellent, detailed reference for disassembling and reassembling the Beretta Mod 92.  The step-by-step video is very well done and I'm very pleased with the DVD.
